Subject: drm/amdgpu: Iterate through DRM connectors correctly
MIME-Version: 1.0
Content-Type: text/plain; charset=UTF-8
Content-Transfer-Encoding: 8bit
Git-commit: f8d2d39eb406946546d71e5869b04d99fa094834
